{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place pecans in mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 4<b>. Transfer to a bowl and place on mixing bowl lid. Weigh in raisins then set aside.","Place buckwheat in mixing bowl and grind <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add almond milk, water, maple syrup and vanilla extract then cook <b>10 min\/90°C\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides and base of mixing bowl with spatula then cook again <b>10 min\/90°C\/speed 3<b>. Pour into bowls, top with raisin-nut mixture and drizzle with maple syrup then serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["40 g pecan nuts","60 g raisins","200 g buckwheat grains","500 g almond milk, or milk of choice","450 g water","20 g maple syrup, plus extra for serving","1 tsp vanilla extract"]}],"id":"r148367","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-90JOZJuuQ98\/XZafTeLFH9I\/AAAAAAAAgtA\/R8sq5tXgTFUPmyPw4RK5rS1uLaxTr-qkQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_k_BZ-8qhL1FMb75Y.png","title":"Buckwheat Porridge","publishedAt":"2017-03-20T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"17.1 g","fat":"36.8 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"116.6 g","calories":"3623 kJ \/ 866 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl, serving bowls","basicInfo":["easy","5m","25m","8 portions"]}